[{"short_id":"fzce4h","created_at":"2026-05-21T10:53:05.000-05:00","title":"Ursula: thread-per-core, multi-Raft Rust runtime for HTTP event streams","url":"https://github.com/tonbo-io/ursula","score":1,"flags":0,"comment_count":1,"description":"\u003cp\u003eHi folks, I just open-sourced Ursula, a self-hosted, multi-node server for HTTP event streams built on ElectricSQL's Durable Streams Protocol.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eArchitecture summary:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ethread-per-core x multi-Raft\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ein-memory hot ring on the write path, S3 as cold tier\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ewrites commit at Raft quorum in sub-50ms\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eArchitecture: \u003ca href=\"https://ursula.tonbo.io/docs/architecture/overview\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003ehttps://ursula.tonbo.io/docs/architecture/overview\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBenchmark with Raft quorum:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e5.9x writes vs the Node.js Durable Streams by official, 5.2x vs S2 Lite\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e6.1ms p99 SSE fan-out to 1000 subscribers (160x lower than DS reference, 18x lower than S2 Lite)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReplication based on multi-Raft quorum mode suffers minimal durability loss compared to S3\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eUrsula on 3 x c7g.4xlarge, baselines on 1 x c7g.4xlarge.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFull methodology: \u003ca href=\"https://ursula.tonbo.io/benchmark\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003ehttps://ursula.tonbo.io/benchmark\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"Hi folks, I just open-sourced Ursula, a self-hosted, multi-node server for HTTP event streams built on ElectricSQL's Durable Streams Protocol.\r\n\r\nArchitecture summary:\r\n- thread-per-core x multi-Raft\r\n- in-memory hot ring on the write path, S3 as cold tier\r\n- writes commit at Raft quorum in sub-50ms\r\n\r\nArchitecture: https://ursula.tonbo.io/docs/architecture/overview\r\n\r\nBenchmark with Raft quorum:\r\n- 5.9x writes vs the Node.js Durable Streams by official, 5.2x vs S2 Lite\r\n- 6.1ms p99 SSE fan-out to 1000 subscribers (160x lower than DS reference, 18x lower than S2 Lite)\r\n- Replication based on multi-Raft quorum mode suffers minimal durability loss compared to S3\r\n\r\n*Ursula on 3 x c7g.4xlarge, baselines on 1 x c7g.4xlarge.*\r\n\r\nFull methodology: https://ursula.tonbo.io/benchmark","submitter_user":"yochow","user_is_author":true,"tags":["distributed"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/fzce4h","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/fzce4h/ursula_thread_per_core_multi_raft_rust"},{"short_id":"gl13es","created_at":"2026-05-21T10:35:29.000-05:00","title":"John Regehr's Integers in C Quiz","url":"https://acepace.net/integerQuiz/","score":2,"flags":0,"comment_count":0,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"kenballus","user_is_author":false,"tags":["c"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/gl13es","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/gl13es/john_regehr_s_integers_c_quiz"},{"short_id":"r87zln","created_at":"2026-05-21T10:09:32.000-05:00","title":"Internships for early university / no former employment","url":"","score":7,"flags":0,"comment_count":4,"description":"\u003cp\u003eAs a rising freshman beginning an undergraduate computer science degree this fall, I wonder what internship opportunities (FOSS preferred) are there, for applicants in early university or who otherwise have no former employment experience (despite, perhaps, contributions to FOSS).\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePossible template, adapted from previous \u003ccode\u003et/job\u003c/code\u003e posts:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cpre\u003e\u003ccode\u003e**Company:** XYZ\r\n\r\n**Company website:** WWW\r\n\r\n**Position(s):** ABC\r\n\r\n**Target applicant pool:** XXX (for example, \"graduating in 2030\", \"any undergraduate pursuing a degree in CS/etc\", etc.)\r\n\r\n**Duration:** XXX\r\n\r\n**Location:** XXX (please include whether REMOTE worldwide/US/EU/etc or ONSITE)\r\n\r\n**Description:** XYZ\r\n\r\n**Tech stack:** ABC\r\n\r\n**Compensation:** XXX\r\n\r\n**Contacts:** WWW\r\n\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI think comments other than listings (e.g., advice and such) should also be welcome here!\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"As a rising freshman beginning an undergraduate computer science degree this fall, I wonder what internship opportunities (FOSS preferred) are there, for applicants in early university or who otherwise have no former employment experience (despite, perhaps, contributions to FOSS).\r\n\r\nPossible template, adapted from previous `t/job` posts:\r\n\r\n```\r\n**Company:** XYZ\r\n\r\n**Company website:** WWW\r\n\r\n**Position(s):** ABC\r\n\r\n**Target applicant pool:** XXX (for example, \"graduating in 2030\", \"any undergraduate pursuing a degree in CS/etc\", etc.)\r\n\r\n**Duration:** XXX\r\n\r\n**Location:** XXX (please include whether REMOTE worldwide/US/EU/etc or ONSITE)\r\n\r\n**Description:** XYZ\r\n\r\n**Tech stack:** ABC\r\n\r\n**Compensation:** XXX\r\n\r\n**Contacts:** WWW\r\n```\r\n\r\nI think comments other than listings (e.g., advice and such) should also be welcome here!","submitter_user":"runxiyu","user_is_author":true,"tags":["ask","job"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/r87zln","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/r87zln/internships_for_early_university_no"},{"short_id":"ofd0cf","created_at":"2026-05-21T10:00:09.000-05:00","title":"KotlinConf’26 Keynote Highlights: Advances in Language Design, Tooling, AI-Driven Workflows, and Multiplatform Development | The Kotlin Blog","url":"https://blog.jetbrains.com/kotlin/2026/05/kotlinconf26-keynote-highlights/","score":1,"flags":0,"comment_count":0,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"snej","user_is_author":false,"tags":["kotlin"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/ofd0cf","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/ofd0cf/kotlinconf_26_keynote_highlights"},{"short_id":